    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "July 8, 1952",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Robinson, Illinois",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "Mr. J. Edgar Hoover, Director",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "Federal Bureau of Investigation",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Washington, District of Columbia",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Perhaps this is a little out of your line of endeavor, however, I feel that per-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "haps you or your organization might be able to give me some information concerning",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "the following matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "From the first time it was written up in the press I have been keenly interested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "in strange celestial phenomena such as the flying disks popularly called \"flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "saucers.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Now out of all the thousands of people who have reported sightings not all of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "them have had too much to drink, nor could they have been victims of optical",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "illusions, retinal retention, or hallucinations. Some of the objects sighted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "could not have been jet craft, guided missiles, or rockets, neither could they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "all have been weather instruments. Unretouched and undoctored photographs have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "given evidence that someone must have seen something.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "It seems that both civil and military authorities are most willing to proclaim",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "what the objects are not. I feel there is more to the matter than meets the eye.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "My decision to write you was based on the thought I would get straight answers.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "Do you have any ideas or data on this subject? What are your opinions? If not,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "where might I write for such information? Any kindness, consideration, or in-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "formation which you can extend toward me concerning this matter will certainly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "be most sincerely appreciated.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "Very truly yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "status": "blank"
    },
